prediction.sparql:
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#>
SELECT ?property ?propertyLabel ?value WHERE {
  wd:Q64 ?property ?value .
  ?property rdfs:label ?propertyLabel
  FILTER ( LANG( ?propertyLabel ) = 'en' ) .
}
LIMIT 100

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?german ?spouse WHERE {
  ?german wdt:P27 wd:Q183 ; wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  ?spouse wdt:P31 wd:Q82955 .
}
LIMIT 10

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?daughter ?spouse WHERE {
  wd:Q25310 wdt:P40 ?daughter .
  ?daughter wdt:P21 wd:Q6581072 .
  ?daughter wdt:P26 ?spouse .
  FILTER ( ?daughter = wd:Q273833 )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q5513 wdt:P2046 ?baikalArea .
  wd:Q5525 wdt:P2046 ?bearArea .
  FILTER ( ?baikalArea > ?bearArea )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
ASK {
  wd:Q128160 wdt:P580 ?cubanMissileCrisisDate .
  wd:Q128161 wdt:P580 ?bayOfPigsInvasionDate .
  FILTER ( ?cubanMissileCrisisDate < ?bayOfPigsInvasionDate )
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX ps: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/statement/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
ASK WHERE {
  wd:Q11817 p:P607 ?statement .
  ?statement ps:P607 wd:Q26013 .
}

PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
SELECT ?episode WHERE {
  ?episode wdt:P179 wd:Q23628 .
  ?episode wdt:P361 ?season .
  ?season wdt:P31 wd:Q13442814 .
  ?season wdt:P3771 '1' .
  ?episode wdt:P1545 ?episodeNumber
}

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
SELECT ?country ( COUNT( ?cave ) AS ?caveCount ) WHERE {
  ?cave wdt:P31 wd:Q35509 .
  ?cave wdt:P17 ?country
}
GROUP BY ?country
HAVING ( COUNT( ?cave ) > 10 )
ORDER BY DESC ( ?caveCount )

PREFIX wd: <http://www.wikidata.org/entity/>
PREFIX wdt: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/direct/>
PREFIX pq: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/qualifier/>
PREFIX p: <http://www.wikidata.org/prop/>
SELECT ?date WHERE {
  wd:Q211 wdt:P463 wd:Q458 .
  wd:Q211 p:P463 ?stmt .
  ?stmt pq:P580 ?date
}
ORDER BY ?date
LIMIT 1
